      "link": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "jS0nuwUS9VR76vPOlLqzK",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 555.4406518103262,
      "y": 3347.9547018118546,
      "width": 1045.9794921875,
      "height": 405,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#cdd6f4",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0t4",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2089181581,
      "version": 584,
      "versionNonce": 1011837443,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1780521344782,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "3.  They decided to put java in the browser, but java was too \n     heavyweight for small page interactions So they decided \n     to use java as the main language by creating java applets \n     that would handle heavy tasks like \n                                             Game, Chart Tool, Calculator App etc. \n     And create a lightweight scripting language for the browser \n     that would be a helper language for handling \n                                             Button Click, Form Validation, \n                                             Change Text, Show/Hide Menu etc.",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "3.  They decided to put java in the browser, but java was too \n     heavyweight for small page interactions So they decided \n     to use java as the main language by creating java applets \n     that would handle heavy tasks like \n                                             Game, Chart Tool, Calculator App etc. \n     And create a lightweight scripting language for the browser \n     that would be a helper language for handling \n                                             Button Click, Form Validation, \n                                             Change Text, Show/Hide Menu etc.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "EjYxmEV-MoDAX24N1LmZB",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 623.6459791993591,
      "y": 3866.233944494128,
      "width": 975.49169921875,
      "height": 225,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#cdd6f4",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0t8",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1111912461,
      "version": 16,
      "versionNonce": 37120941,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1780521344782,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Then Brendan Eich( an engineer of netscape) wrote the \nprototype in roughly ten days in May 1995. \nIt was named Livescript first but then changed to JavaScript \nto borrow Java’s fame, even though the two languages are \nlargely unrelated",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Then Brendan Eich( an engineer of netscape) wrote the \nprototype in roughly ten days in May 1995. \nIt was named Livescript first but then changed to JavaScript \nto borrow Java’s fame, even though the two languages are \nlargely unrelated",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "NP15km_-ymKxGkXucMzNn",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 618.8654060456836,
      "y": 4157.064834413961,
      "width": 938.8077392578125,
      "height": 180,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#cdd6f4",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0tA",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 188136963,
      "version": 63,
      "versionNonce": 863580579,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1780521344782,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "That single business decision “make it look like Java” \nis what ruled out simply adopting Python or Perl, \nwhich existed and would have fit. \nThe best technical choice lost to a marketing requirement.",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "That single business decision “make it look like Java” \nis what ruled out simply adopting Python or Perl, \nwhich existed and would have fit. \nThe best technical choice lost to a marketing requirement.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "zWEUnnG7JunVZGgkaMEXS",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 664.7499428083158,
      "y": 5326.7305487881895,
      "width": 961.8836669921875,
      "height": 90,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#f38ba8",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0tC",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1659634573,
      "version": 185,
      "versionNonce": 1093037581,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1780521344782,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Java eventually disappeared from browsers, \nwhile JavaScript became rthe primary language of the web.",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Java eventually disappeared from browsers, \nwhile JavaScript became rthe primary language of the web.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
