    },
    {
      "id": "JUmlDoY08XY-4GvmwFRKX",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 531.8470539603829,
      "y": 17205.24594948641,
      "width": 788.687744140625,
      "height": 90,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#cdd6f4",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b4aO",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1594666466,
      "version": 27,
      "versionNonce": 1198885794,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1780582652580,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "A. This code could read/write/delete any file on\nyour machine",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "A. This code could read/write/delete any file on your machine",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "HwAarNk5VktDBScmDGyEQ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1461.433148407928,
      "y": 17193.8570509094,
      "width": 793.0078125,
      "height": 135,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#cdd6f4",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b4aQ",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 397908386,
      "version": 44,
      "versionNonce": 1026815870,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1780582652580,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "A. You’d have to intercept all file I/O calls and\neither block them or restrict them to a safe\n“virtual” file system",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "A. You’d have to intercept all file I/O calls and either block them or restrict them to a safe “virtual” file system",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "B3GM2jxbKxmJHoNh75q9Z",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 526.8545656442556,
      "y": 17453.142763916818,
      "width": 834.2277221679688,
      "height": 45,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#cdd6f4",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b4aS",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 187810942,
      "version": 43,
      "versionNonce": 1506264930,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1780582652580,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "B. Raw C++ can call system() to run OS commands.",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "B. Raw C++ can call system() to run OS commands.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "OzPv3_ycTW8wNUqw0f2QI",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1456.0953144584296,
      "y": 17435.126842460348,
      "width": 794.1597290039062,
      "height": 135,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#cdd6f4",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b4aV",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1878982498,
      "version": 51,
      "versionNonce": 1560565694,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1780582652580,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "B. Sandboxing would mean completely disabling\nor trapping such calls, otherwise a website could\nliterally wipe your drive.",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "B. Sandboxing would mean completely disabling or trapping such calls, otherwise a website could literally wipe your drive.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "F55z_hwLM4c75KYTA89np",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 519.5855183158518,
      "y": 17646.238118269495,
      "width": 775.11572265625,
      "height": 135,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#cdd6f4",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b4aX",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 604034302,
      "version": 34,
      "versionNonce": 635210530,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1780582652580,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "C. C++ allows arbitrary pointer arithmetic →\ncould overwrite OS/kernel memory or peek into\nsensitive regions.",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "C. C++ allows arbitrary pointer arithmetic → could overwrite OS/kernel memory or peek into sensitive regions.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "EEzcDvvbT-vQr-Pqb4WQK",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1461.9614905186977,
      "y": 17635.126929653426,
      "width": 763.3796997070312,
      "height": 135,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#cdd6f4",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b4aZ",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 12921954,
      "version": 58,
      "versionNonce": 475967486,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1780582652580,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "C. In a sandbox, you’d have to rewrite the\nruntime so pointers never escape into raw\nmachine addresses.",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "C. In a sandbox, you’d have to rewrite the runtime so pointers never escape into raw machine addresses.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "t8SBwmeOgOjGWErDkl0-_",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 524.7349410976597,
      "y": 17894.134845506833,
      "width": 748.9437255859375,
      "height": 90,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#cdd6f4",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b4ab",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1891860002,
      "version": 50,
      "versionNonce": 1646450402,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1780582652580,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "D. C++ can open arbitrary sockets, bypassing\nthe browser’s control.",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "D. C++ can open arbitrary sockets, bypassing the browser’s control.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "6MNFPS_vLvfU-LTQjybXJ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1468.244972661555,
      "y": 17863.69826975348,
      "width": 734.9397583007812,
      "height": 135,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#cdd6f4",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b4ad",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1936175550,
      "version": 47,
      "versionNonce": 1732509758,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1780582652580,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "D. Sandboxing would require blocking direct\nsocket creation and only allowing browser-\ncontrolled HTTP requests.",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "D. Sandboxing would require blocking direct socket creation and only allowing browser-controlled HTTP requests.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "bZ2y6aHNyQ5Y7QBYg7yB9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 773.3337831735527,
      "y": 18721.23798172757,
      "width": 34.16398620605469,
      "height": 45,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#cdd6f4",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b4af",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 444579554,
      "version": 13,
      "versionNonce": 522824354,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1780582652580,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "JS",
      "fontSize": 36,
